Wasserstein Debt Opportunities Offshore Fund, Ltd.  Financing
Wasserstein Debt Opportunities Offshore Fund, Ltd. just submitted form D announcing  Indefinite financing.  Wasserstein Debt Opportunities Offshore Fund, Ltd. was able to sell $7,550,000. The total private offering amount was Indefinite. The financing was made by 4 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $100,000. The financing document was filed on 2015-10-16. Wasserstein Debt Opportunities Offshore Fund, Ltd. is based in  1301 AVENUE OF THE AMERICAS, 41ST FLOOR  NEW YORK 10019. The firm's business is Pooled Investment Fund. The form was signed by  Robert Mersten.





