Wasserstein & Co. |  About Wasserstein Partners About Wasserstein Partners

				With over 20 years of trusted investment experience, Wasserstein Partners focuses on mid-market leveraged buyout investments in three sectors: Media and Communications, Consumer Products and Water and Industrial.			






Wasserstein Partners conducts its investment activities through the Wasserstein Partners family of funds. Predecessor funds U.S. Equity Partners I and II invested a total of approximately $750 million of equity capital.  Our third fund, Wasserstein Partners III, deployed $750 million of direct equity and co-investment capital.  The firm is currently investing out of its fourth fund, Wasserstein Partners IV, with $790 million of committed capital.
We invest on behalf of a diverse and prominent group of limited partners spread across investor classes and geographies:





American Seafoods Group






All Clad



 



 



